short_description: Age of Innocence is a European footwear brand for girls from 0 to 8.The philosophy of Age of Innocence is all about celebrating childhood and creating lifetime memories. The brand‚Äôs DNA is a combination of femininity, timeless elegance, chic and a slight retro flair with a contemporary twist. The brand draws inspiration from romance, history, vintage baby shoes and paintings of great artists, while adding a contemporary touch for a modern, yet timeless look.An Age of Innocence girl is quintessentially a city girl, romantic and strong, a daydreamer with a very specific point of view.We create shoes that a baby girl would love to wear and something that will be part of her memories as she grows up.
